flowchart TB
  subgraph DeviceSite[Retail store or device site]
    Hardware[DragonBoard or Windows 10 IoT device\nDocumented]
    Cameras[USB cameras\nDocumented/Observed via API use]
    UWP[Retailizer.UWP package\nObserved]
    Cameras --> Hardware
    Hardware --> UWP
  end

  subgraph Provisioned[Azure resource group provisioned by ARM]
    AppPlan[App Service plan\nProvisioned]
    WebApp[Backend Web App\nProvisioned]
    Storage[Storage account\nProvisioned]
    IoTHub[IoT Hub\nProvisioned]
    ServiceBus[Service Bus namespace\nProvisioned]
    Queue[Queue parameter events/event_queue\nConflicting evidence]
    DocAccount[DocumentDB account\nProvisioned]
    FaceAcct[Face API account\nProvisioned]
    EmotionAcct[Emotion API account\nProvisioned only]
  end

  subgraph RequiredNotProvisioned[Required/documented but not provisioned in ARM]
    WebJob[Retailizer.Job WebJob deployment\nObserved source only]
    DBInit[Database and collections\nInitializer-created]
    Container[faces blob container\nInitializer-created]
    PersonGroup[Face person group\nInitializer-created]
    StreamAnalytics[Stream Analytics or route\nDocumented/Inferred, not found]
    PowerBI[Power BI dashboard\nDocumented only]
  end

  AppPlan --> WebApp
  ServiceBus --> Queue
  UWP -->|registration HTTP| WebApp
  UWP -->|blob upload| Storage
  UWP -->|device-to-cloud messages| IoTHub
  IoTHub -. missing route implementation .-> StreamAnalytics
  StreamAnalytics -. expected queue output .-> Queue
  WebJob --> Queue
  WebJob --> Storage
  WebJob --> DocAccount
  WebJob --> FaceAcct
  DBInit --> DocAccount
  Container --> Storage
  PersonGroup --> FaceAcct
  DocAccount -. dataset unknown .-> PowerBI
  EmotionAcct -. no observed application use .-> WebJob
